questions.quote: Say Ross, when you picture Phoebe living on the street, is she surrounded by the entire cast of Annie?
No, you can't go there! You know how I feel about these "big massage places"! They're putting people like me out of business!
Why? It's just that I've waited seven years for an opportunity like this, and you can't even wait four and a half minutes for a stupid onion tartlet?
Wow! That didn't take long. I thought you said Tulsa was, like a three hour flight.
No, it's not supposed to be funny, it's supposed to be scary.
OK, guys, guys? I have the definitive one. Mwwwooooo-hah-hah...
Oh, I just remembered. We do have something to eat. Monica put something in our oven this morning.
Oh, yeah, ok. Let me just grab my night vision goggles and my stun gun.
A new grocery store. The universe said I was going to meet a nice guy and that's what they gave me? When I get up there I'm going to kick some ass.
Oh, well, er, I already ate, but sure...! Guess what happened at work today...
